lead_paragraph: After beating the 'best team in the world', playing lowly Middlesbrough on a November afternoon in the north of England should bring Premier League leaders Manchester City nicely back to earth.

headline.print_headline: From Barcelona to 'Boro, Man City Go Back to Basics
